Packed with a powerful punch of high alcohol hoppiness, Triple IPAs will definitely hit you hard. Often featuring a sweet flavor profile, these boozy brews can sneak up on you.  That's 15 different beers with the style of IPA - Triple. Try 5 more for Level 4!
